import React, { Component, Fragment } from 'react'; import Navbar from '../../UI/Navbar'; import '../../../App.css'; class NarcoticUnit extends Component { render () { return (
Narcotic Unit

The Narcotics Unit consists of a number of specialized units. The MNVP (Major Narcotic Vendor Prosecution) Unit consists of attorneys who handle all high-level narcotics sales, possession for sale and manufacturing cases. The MNVP prosecutor works closely with law enforcement for MNVP unit prosecution. The MNVP prosecutors directly review search and arrest warrants, and discusses search / case issues in advance. As a vertical prosecution unit, it endeavors to keep major dealers in custody pending the conclusion of the case and seeks maximum penalties for these drug sellers.

The GDFT (General Drug Felony Team) consists of additional attorneys north and south who work with county narcotics task forces, individual agency narcotic units and routine law enforcement cases. These attorneys handle street level / possession for sales and possession cases.
